Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.63,0:00:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓抑高昂的鼓動 奔向暮色昏暗的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.57,0:00:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心和客套之間 對那傢伙的想法複雜交錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.15,0:00:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.95,0:00:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這份愛粉身碎骨 你的表情為何如此寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.89,0:00:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謊言 心機 嫉妒 背叛 有如家常便飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.50,0:00:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無須大驚小怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃之心點燃火苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.21,0:00:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想再去見你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.44,0:00:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不行動 何時才要做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.25,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.25,0:00:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.29,0:01:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅的 優美的 華麗的飛舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.39,0:01:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薔薇花開 薔薇花飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.50,0:01:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈禱的話 一定能改變命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.67,0:01:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒熱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.74,0:01:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得燦爛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.78,0:01:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.89,0:01:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第10話 北斗傳人之戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.17,0:02:10.18,CM,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;15;0;0,fosky fansub小組提醒：本字幕僅供學習交流使用,請勿用於商業用途否則因此產生的一切後果請自負　　片源&壓制:海馬　ocr&校對:99019901
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.87,0:01:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.11,0:01:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔，鼬鼠陳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.48,0:01:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼晚打來有何貴幹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.28,0:02:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？牢房的警衛是內奸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡竟然會有青幫的漏網之魚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.33,0:02:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳兄弟，你怎麼了？\N又有人被槍擊了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.30,0:02:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦，我才沒有帶槍咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.40,0:02:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事，沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說靈王已經來上海啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對，不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王剛才打電話來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他說要自己找出閻王的下落\N結果擅自跑走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.72,0:02:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之，我告訴他你的住址了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.13,0:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要在這裡等着\N拿閻王的人頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.10,0:02:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人頭，人頭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:02:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.09,0:03:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家美玉已經是大明星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.53,0:03:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今才告訴她\N以前的情人潘老大還活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.96,0:03:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要求她去引誘吳出來\N我實在是說不出口啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.63,0:03:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美玉已經跟我們\N是不同世界的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.27,0:03:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要再將她牽扯進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潘也不希望我這樣做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.58,0:03:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.05,0:03:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要美玉稍微邀一下\N那傢伙一定會現身的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.88,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是去請她暗中幫我們吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.69,0:03:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不對勁的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.00,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…\N全身包繃帶的司機也太怪了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿幫了？我們穿幫了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，原來是基斯上校啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.69,0:04:27.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要通知你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.23,0:04:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違規停車嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.17,0:04:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是紅華會吳東來的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.81,0:04:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王的人頭來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.52,0:04:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一封請帖寄來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.72,0:04:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳東來3天後會出現在大戲院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.03,0:05:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊美玉叫我來通知你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我和她是舊識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.30,0:05:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她邀請吳去參加她的生日派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.00,0:05:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楊…美玉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說這個就當作是\N上次誤會你的道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.48,0:05:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看穿拳的心意了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.72,0:05:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.68,0:05:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這種大人物來找我\N只為了傳話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.89,0:05:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很聰明嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.62,0:05:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有件事要通知你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.26,0:05:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽好，吳的身邊有靈王保護他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.13,0:05:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是北斗孫家拳的高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.50,0:05:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗孫家拳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.50,0:05:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼連這種事都知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是7年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時嵩山少林寺失火…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧侶們想從火場搶救出大量經典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.82,0:06:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他們眼前所看到的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.09,0:06:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是門房大開\N以及被清空的地下密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而當時遭盜走的秘傳書當中\N有寫着關於北斗三家拳法的記載
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.87,0:06:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗三家拳的事…\N你應該也很清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.05,0:06:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在三國時代的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.42,0:06:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗神拳為了守護三分天下的\N孫，曹，劉三國的各家英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而分成了三個派別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.43,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而現在三家拳之一\N北斗孫家拳的靈王現身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴我這些事是想幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.12,0:07:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒別的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.35,0:07:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能說我對東方這套\N被稱為拳法的殺人秘技很感興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再問你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼知道我們在這裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:25.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看看自己的樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.74,0:07:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟蹤和偽裝都太顯眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.41,0:07:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎參加楊美玉小姐的生日派對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好盛大的派對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.30,0:07:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N能被楊美玉邀請，真是好榮幸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派對真的好豪華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基斯上校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.79,0:08:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.82,0:08:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.73,0:08:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會白費妳一番苦心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.06,0:08:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙一定會潛入這裡\N找吳算帳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那道光芒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.64,0:08:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光芒的確有些詭異\N跟平常不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.58,0:08:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎恐怕會有危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.05,0:08:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王應該也潛入這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.65,0:08:46.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王來了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.39,0:08:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.73,0:09:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.44,0:09:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服脫下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.34,0:09:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你，脫衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.68,0:09:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.92,0:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定不會穿幫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,善後的事就交給你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.54,0:09:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:36.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…\N我沒見過那麼凶狠的服務生耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了，吳東來到了\N我們也動身吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.59,0:10:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個楊美玉終於想主動啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.90,0:10:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳老大\N美玉一定是對您有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.53,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可是主賓耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.84,0:10:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯，她還真是可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總算明白男人不能光看外表了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去說給潘聽聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦，來啦，來啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精力整個來啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜晚上…嘿咻，嘿咻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻，嘿咻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.30,0:10:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託楊美玉的福\N老大暫時不會拿槍亂射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.77,0:10:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真感謝美玉大小姐啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.21,0:10:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是主賓專用的簽到處嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走，突擊前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.34,0:10:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻，嘿咻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生日禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吳老大這份大禮真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.16,0:11:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點收下吧，快點收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，一點小意思\N金條10條而已啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，請您在這邊簽到一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說“千刀”？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.58,0:11:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是簽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.55,0:11:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是讓上海有如星辰的貴客們\N簽到用的芳名簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.55,0:11:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這對楊美玉小姐來說\N會是她一生的寶物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.66,0:11:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大根本不會寫字耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個豬頭想找死嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們快看，老大在硬坳了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了，老大生平第一次握筆耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.34,0:11:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大加油，您一定能辦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.74,0:11:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？他是在施什麼咒語嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.32,0:12:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.02,0:12:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說我沒握過槍以外的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.69,0:12:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎？\N你在拖拖拉拉什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.46,0:12:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，麻煩你動作快一點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.63,0:12:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了槍以外沒握過其他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.20,0:12:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會連名字都不會寫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.74,0:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你不會寫字啊？不會嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.08,0:12:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你乾脆畫海獅上去好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.85,0:12:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記號，畫記號就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫一個海獅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個王八蛋\N你是說我長得像海獅？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W…WHY？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WHY你個頭，我才不是海獅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.97,0:13:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是海獅…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.23,0:13:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是海獅啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.73,0:13:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼看都不像服務生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.85,0:13:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，那個槍聲難不成是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.69,0:13:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經揭開序幕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.89,0:13:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗之星交會之時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.53,0:13:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便是天之將亡的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.80,0:14:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混蛋\N都把老子當白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.84,0:14:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.88,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乒乒砰砰吵死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.25,0:14:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果真的是服務生\N就該去制止客人喧嘩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.78,0:14:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正等一下子彈自然就會射完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰敢攔我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.97,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閻王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.89,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王也在這裡啊，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.02,0:14:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然就是靈王啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種就過來啊，閻王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.76,0:15:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子才不怕你咧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.83,0:15:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈王，快收拾他\N讓他見識北斗不是只有他一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.35,0:15:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，不是我，是對付他啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.48,0:15:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙太吵了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的決鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.49,0:15:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你憑什麼命令我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於安靜下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.35,0:15:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你借過一下好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.79,0:16:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想問那個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.52,0:16:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想問潘光琳的下落嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你可以直接問我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他現在在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.00,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你的說法來看\N潘是真的還活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，他還在苟延殘喘着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少兩小時之前是這樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.58,0:16:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吳東來就沒有用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准放水啊，閻王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗孫家拳的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.76,0:17:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操氣術嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.57,0:17:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着換你讓我見識一下…\N北斗神拳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到我會在這裡遇到\N同為北斗分支的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不應該發生的宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.75,0:17:35.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是生於亂世中的北斗宿命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.39,0:17:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個，快把吳抬走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.66,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這裡\N我可不能保證他的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.97,0:18:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，你想問出潘的下落\N就只能選擇打倒我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.07,0:18:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…北斗神拳應該可以\N輕易逼人非自願的招供
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.55,0:18:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你得先碰得到我才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大…\N吳老大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.80,0:18:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點啊…\N老大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:35.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他…他死掉了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.58,0:18:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快死啊，最好死掉算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他死翹翹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.55,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為呼吸都停止了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.36,0:18:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後都不用擔心被掃射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝上天啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還沒死？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？什麼叫我還沒死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.97,0:19:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，您沒死真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.14,0:19:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，怎麼這麼衰啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.48,0:19:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，吳逃走了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳不知道發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.29,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的槍聲，難道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你說話啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.16,0:19:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,子英，男人不該為了小事窮緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳一定可以平安歸來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要耐心等他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.37,0:19:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了最後一刻能够幫他的\N就只有我們倆而已了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.65,0:19:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳志郎對靈王…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.32,0:19:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.68,0:19:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下北斗傳人之戰吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.24,0:20:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.54,0:20:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然連我的氣都能吸取\N你的操氣術果然不簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次和北斗神拳交手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想先用北斗孫家拳 . 操氣掌\N來削弱你的氣力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就來吧\N我的氣你就儘管吸走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.83,0:20:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你承受得住的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.64,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.27,0:20:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你運功積蓄了多少氣\N全部都會被我吸走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是北斗交戰的場面嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.90,0:21:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行\N美玉繼續待在這裡會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.01,0:21:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後掌握星耀光輝的究竟會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.26,0:22:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳該不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳…拳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.05,0:22:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手被折斷了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.28,0:22:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好痛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.62,0:22:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又在亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.39,0:22:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，我搞清楚潘在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.66,0:22:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.10,0:22:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差點忘了拳的鼻子比狗還靈敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.53,0:22:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有線索了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.63,0:22:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，靈王身上有潘的味道\N還有他所在地的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.57,0:23:03.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧，去見我們的朋友了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他知道潘在哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.16,0:23:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗傳人的對戰就是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.30,0:23:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次可不是斷個手臂就能了事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.84,0:23:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗傳人終於對上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.74,0:23:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在某個夜晚看到發光的金人\N從東方飛翔而來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.18,0:23:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是天帝的旨意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.28,0:23:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天啊，您對亂世中的北斗之拳\N究竟有何企圖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.29,0:23:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗的命運，是正還是反？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.18,0:24:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂靜安眠的城市中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.51,0:24:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁陷入深深沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.55,0:24:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有許多瑣碎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.46,0:24:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒錯過妳瞬間的不安神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.26,0:24:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳是不是已經不再愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.30,0:24:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有答案就等於是答案了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.87,0:24:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在那種時候與妳相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:44.74,0:24:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會像被冰凍一般無法言語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.65,0:24:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.35,0:24:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳好比四散的蝴蝶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.16,0:25:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成微風與色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.29,0:25:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳爆裂飛散出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.17,0:25:16.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有如蝴蝶從我心中遠去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.68,0:25:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有妳 我的一切都將停擺
